Health status, trends, and issues in Sri Lanka.

Jayasekara RS(1), Schultz T.

Author information:
(1)Discipline of Nursing, JBI Research Unit, School of Population Health and 
Clinical Practice, The University of Adelaide, Adelaide, SA 5005, Australia. 
