compared with waiting for a standard kidney (5.3 yr) or a living donation (5.5 
yr) after 4 yr of dialysis. Conversely, younger recipients (18 to 39 yr) had 
longer life expectancy with a living donation (27.6 yr) or standard kidney (26.4 
